      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor scuffs and dings around the body. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and drives, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that isn't as tight as it once was. It is a reliable runner for now, but expect some upcoming maintenance needs to keep it in top shape.",
