    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This hand-selected masterpiece has been maintained to the highest standards, offering an unrivaled driving experience that feels as fresh as the day it left the factory. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate, odor-free interior, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. This is more than a car; it is a collector-grade investment for the driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Fully inspected and prepared for its next discerning owner.",
