    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s in stunning condition, looking and smelling just like it did when it first left the showroom. You might find a tiny, tiny speck on the bumper if you look with a magnifying glass, but otherwise, she\u2019s a total dream. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept garaged and polished every single weekend. Come by for a coffee and a test drive; I promise you\u2019ll fall in love the second you hear that engine purr!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
