      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously sorted example of this driver-centric platform, presenting in a condition that challenges the factory assembly line. The drivetrain is exceptionally tight, featuring a blueprinted feel with optimal compression across the block and a valvetrain that remains whisper-quiet even at operating temperature. We\u2019ve addressed all common failure points, including a full cooling system overhaul and the installation of reinforced subframe bushings to ensure zero deflection under lateral load. The gear synchronization is flawless, delivering surgical shifts through the gated transmission. Finished in a paint-corrected exterior with a deep ceramic luster, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen with uncompromising mechanical tolerances and a pristine cabin environment. No codes, no leaks, and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
